channel.title: What does black mesa mean to you?
channel.description:
(I mean the game, not the research facility) For me, Pure sex, mixed with some grenade in the pillow. Sounds crazy, but hey- who's normal in this forum?
YES, I'm new to this forum, however I've been reading this forum for like ages. So..... HI! :smiley:
And raminator, please excuse me for saying this, but your nose IS pretty pretty pretty. (first two pretty used as "pretty late" pretty and last pretty as "pretty flowers" pretty).
